metadata.title: Nordic Ware 3-D Summer Series Cookie Cutter Set
features: 3-dimensional summer-themed cookie cutter set makes 6 standup shapes
12 bright blue plastic cutters with customized stands
Packaged in sturdy cardboard storage box
description: Create festive birthday cookies with our whimsical 3-D stand-up cookie cutters. Six fun shapes including a teddy bear, unicorn, airplane, sailboat, dolphin and dinosaur! Set comes with a cardboard storage box and a recipe for sugar cookies and icing. Proudly made in the USA by Nordic Ware.

Rainy July days are made for cozy baking projects at home, and the kids will love NordicWare's 3-D Summer Series cookie cutter set to bake, decorate, and design their own seasonal diorama. With twelve pieces total, the set makes six standup shapes including a boat, unicorn, dinosaur, teddy bear, airplane, and dolphin. The blue plastic tools are child- and food-friendly, so everyone can participate. Each cutter measures approximately 4 to 5 inches, and the cardboard storage box includes a cookie and icing recipe. When the work is done and stomachs start to growl, all that's left to do is pour cold glasses of milk and dive in!
